1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,000
Sehemu ya 1: Misingi ya Kuagiza kwa Kijapani

2
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:05,533
Samahani.

3
00:00:05,556 --> 00:00:08,789
Tafadhali, naomba menyu.

4
00:00:08,812 --> 00:00:10,949
Ndiyo.

5
00:00:10,973 --> 00:00:14,673
Hii ndiyo menyu yako.

6
00:00:14,696 --> 00:00:17,430
Asante.

7
00:00:17,453 --> 00:00:22,420
Naomba maji pia, tafadhali.

8
00:00:22,443 --> 00:00:25,143
Sawa.

9
00:00:25,166 --> 00:00:28,704
Nitakuletea mara moja.

10
00:00:28,728 --> 00:00:31,161
Samahani.

11
00:00:31,184 --> 00:00:34,287
Tafadhali, naomba kuagiza.

12
00:00:34,311 --> 00:00:36,577
Ndiyo.

13
00:00:36,600 --> 00:00:39,434
Umeamua?

14
00:00:39,457 --> 00:00:43,090
Nitakula kile kile chakula hiki.

15
00:00:43,113 --> 00:00:46,346
Seti ya chakula cha hambaaga, ndiyo?

16
00:00:46,369 --> 00:00:48,403
Ndiyo.

17
00:00:48,426 --> 00:00:53,139
Naomba unirudishe chakula kinachoombwa zaidi.

18
00:00:53,163 --> 00:00:57,196
Saladi ya mboga za msimu inapendwa sana.

19
00:00:57,219 --> 00:01:01,358
Basi, nitakula hiyo pia.

20
00:01:01,382 --> 00:01:04,015
Sawa.

21
00:01:04,038 --> 00:01:07,072
Choo kiko wapi?

22
00:01:07,095 --> 00:01:10,595
Kiko nyuma pale.

23
00:01:10,618 --> 00:01:13,451
Asante.

24
00:01:13,474 --> 00:01:16,390
Umechelewa.

25
00:01:16,413 --> 00:01:19,769
Haya ni chakula chako.

26
00:01:19,793 --> 00:01:22,171
Samahani.

27
00:01:22,195 --> 00:01:26,028
Naweza kuchukua hii nyumbani?

28
00:01:26,051 --> 00:01:27,951
Ndiyo.

29
00:01:27,974 --> 00:01:31,407
Nitakuletea pakiti.

30
00:01:31,430 --> 00:01:35,814
Unaweza kuondoa sahani zilizokwisha tumika?

31
00:01:35,838 --> 00:01:37,938
Ndiyo.

32
00:01:37,961 --> 00:01:40,535
Nitaondoa.

33
00:01:40,558 --> 00:01:43,925
Tafadhali, naomba bili yangu.

34
00:01:43,948 --> 00:01:46,881
Tafadhali nenda kwenye kasha.

35
00:01:46,904 --> 00:01:50,638
Jumla ni yenye 2,500.

36
00:01:50,661 --> 00:01:55,601
Je, tunaweza kulipa kwa njia tofauti na rafiki yangu?

37
00:01:55,624 --> 00:01:57,769
Ndiyo.

38
00:01:57,793 --> 00:02:00,626
Hakuna tatizo.

39
00:02:00,649 --> 00:02:03,649
Sehemu ya 2: Majaribu na Kubadilisha Nguo

40
00:02:03,649 --> 00:02:06,182
Samahani.

41
00:02:06,205 --> 00:02:11,143
Je, unao shati hili kwa rangi tofauti?

42
00:02:11,167 --> 00:02:13,683
Ndiyo.

43
00:02:13,706 --> 00:02:18,206
Tunazo nyeupe na nyeusi.

44
00:02:18,229 --> 00:02:22,823
Naomba nijaribu nyeusi?

45
00:02:22,847 --> 00:02:25,680
Ndiyo.

46
00:02:25,703 --> 00:02:30,470
Tafadhali tumia chumba cha majaribu kule.

47
00:02:30,493 --> 00:02:33,031
Inanifaa vizuri.

48
00:02:33,054 --> 00:02:34,054
Tafadhali nipe hii mpya.

49
00:02:34,077 --> 00:02:37,511
Sawa.

50
00:02:37,534 --> 00:02:41,520
Nitatafuta stoo.

51
00:02:41,543 --> 00:02:46,090
Je, unaweza kunipa bei kidogo rahisi?

52
00:02:46,113 --> 00:02:47,113
Samahani,

53
00:02:47,137 --> 00:02:51,775
hii haijumuishwi katika bei ya uuzaji.

54
00:02:51,798 --> 00:02:54,698
Nimeelewa.

55
00:02:54,721 --> 00:02:55,721
Basi, nitanunua hii.

56
00:02:55,744 --> 00:02:58,777
Asante.

57
00:02:58,800 --> 00:03:06,238
Nitampa rafiki yangu, je unaweza kunikopesha katika pakiti ya zawadi?

58
00:03:06,261 --> 00:03:07,261
Ndiyo,

59
00:03:07,284 --> 00:03:08,284
je, unapendelea pakiti bure ya zawadi?

60
00:03:08,308 --> 00:03:12,008
Ndiyo, tafadhali.

61
00:03:12,031 --> 00:03:16,505
Je, unataka mfuko wa kununulia?

62
00:03:16,528 --> 00:03:17,528
Hapana, nina mfuko wa ekolojia.

63
00:03:17,551 --> 00:03:22,518
Unalipa kwa njia gani?

64
00:03:22,541 --> 00:03:26,500
Je, naweza kulipa kwa kadi ya mkopo?

65
00:03:26,523 --> 00:03:27,523
Ndiyo,

66
00:03:27,546 --> 00:03:30,813
Unaweza kutumia.

67
00:03:30,836 --> 00:03:36,569
Kama ukubwa hautafaa, naweza kurudisha?

68
00:03:36,592 --> 00:03:37,592
Kama una risiti, unaweza kurudisha ndani ya wiki moja.

69
00:03:37,615 --> 00:03:40,615
Sehemu ya 3: Kusonga kwa Barabara na Maombi ya Wateja / Kuelekeza Usafiri na Maombi ya Wateja

70
00:03:40,615 --> 00:03:43,054
Samahani,

71
00:03:43,078 --> 00:03:47,111
Nitapenda kwenda Stesheni ya Tokyo, tafadhali.

72
00:03:47,134 --> 00:03:49,968
Sawa.

73
00:03:49,991 --> 00:03:50,991
Stesheni ya Tokyo upande gani?

74
00:03:51,014 --> 00:03:54,931
Tafadhali, upande wa Yaesu.

75
00:03:54,955 --> 00:03:58,821
Sawa, tunakwenda sasa.

76
00:03:58,844 --> 00:04:02,711
Barabara zina msongamano, sivyo?

77
00:04:02,734 --> 00:04:03,734
Ndiyo,

78
00:04:03,757 --> 00:04:07,862
Jioni kila siku kuna msongamano.

79
00:04:07,885 --> 00:04:08,885
Sina muda, unaweza kuendesha haraka kidogo?

80
00:04:08,908 --> 00:04:11,463
Nimeelewa.

81
00:04:11,487 --> 00:04:15,263
Tutatumia barabara nyingine?

82
00:04:15,286 --> 00:04:18,519
Ndiyo, tafadhali.

83
00:04:18,542 --> 00:04:19,542
Tutafika katika dakika tano hivi.

84
00:04:19,566 --> 00:04:22,364
Asante.

85
00:04:22,387 --> 00:04:23,387
Ee, simama mbele ya duka la huduma hilo.

86
00:04:23,410 --> 00:04:25,881
Hapa ndiyo?

87
00:04:25,905 --> 00:04:26,905
Kiasi ni elfu mbili.

88
00:04:26,928 --> 00:04:27,928
Naweza kulipa kwa kadi ya IC ya usafiri?

89
00:04:27,951 --> 00:04:32,218
Ndiyo, tafadhali pigia.

90
00:04:32,241 --> 00:04:35,756
Nitapenda risiti, tafadhali.

91
00:04:35,779 --> 00:04:39,448
Sawa, hii ndiyo.

92
00:04:39,471 --> 00:04:42,783
Angalia usisahau chochote.

93
00:04:42,806 --> 00:04:43,806
Samahani,

94
00:04:43,830 --> 00:04:44,830
Kwa sababu mizigo yangu ni mingi, unaweza kufungua boneti ya gari?

95
00:04:44,853 --> 00:04:48,720
Ndiyo, nitafungua sasa.

96
00:04:48,743 --> 00:04:51,243
Asante sana.

97
00:04:51,265 --> 00:04:52,265
Endelea na tahadhari.

98
00:04:52,289 --> 00:04:55,289
Sehemu ya 4: Kuingia Kwenye Hoteli / Mchakato wa Kuingia Kwenye Hoteli

99
00:04:55,289 --> 00:04:57,789
Samahani.

100
00:04:57,812 --> 00:05:01,445
Nitapenda kuingia, tafadhali.

101
00:05:01,468 --> 00:05:03,643
Ndiyo.

102
00:05:03,667 --> 00:05:08,334
Tafadhali nipe jina lako lililowekwa akiba.

103
00:05:08,357 --> 00:05:11,116
Smith.

104
00:05:11,139 --> 00:05:14,481
Nitakaa kwa siku tatu.

105
00:05:14,504 --> 00:05:17,460
Bwana Smith, ndiyo.

106
00:05:17,483 --> 00:05:21,617
Tafadhali sahihi hapa.

107
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:28,015
Kabla ya kuingia chumbani, unaweza kukubali mizigo yangu?

108
00:05:28,038 --> 00:05:30,772
Sawa.

109
00:05:30,794 --> 00:05:34,228
Tutakubali hapa.

110
00:05:34,251 --> 00:05:39,924
Samahani, naomba nenosiri la Wi-Fi.

111
00:05:39,948 --> 00:05:43,931
Imeandikwa nyuma ya ufunguo wa chumba.

112
00:05:43,954 --> 00:05:46,787
Asante.

113
00:05:46,810 --> 00:05:50,959
Chakula cha asubuhi kinapatikana saa ngapi?

114
00:05:50,982 --> 00:05:57,139
Tunatoa chakula cha asubuhi kuanzia saa moja asubuhi katika mgahawa wa ghorofa la kwanza.

115
00:05:57,162 --> 00:06:00,029
Nimeelewa.

116
00:06:00,052 --> 00:06:03,202
Chumba chako kiko ghorofa la tano.

117
00:06:03,226 --> 00:06:05,770
Samahani.

118
00:06:05,793 --> 00:06:09,126
Maji moto hayapatikani chumbani.

119
00:06:09,149 --> 00:06:12,317
Samahani sana.

120
00:06:12,340 --> 00:06:15,925
Tutakuja kukagua mara moja.

121
00:06:15,949 --> 00:06:20,616
Pia, naomba taulo moja nyingine.

122
00:06:20,638 --> 00:06:23,472
Sawa.

123
00:06:23,495 --> 00:06:26,264
Tutakuletea.

124
00:06:26,287 --> 00:06:32,987
Kama maji moto hayataweza kurekebishwa, je, naweza kubadilishiwa chumba?

125
00:06:33,010 --> 00:06:36,925
Ndiyo, bila shaka.

126
00:06:36,949 --> 00:06:41,708
Asubuhi ya kesho, tafadhali nipigie teksi.

127
00:06:41,731 --> 00:06:44,365
Sawa.

128
00:06:44,389 --> 00:06:47,582
Saa ngapi utakwenda?

129
00:06:47,606 --> 00:06:51,382
Tafadhali saa mbili.

130
00:06:51,405 --> 00:06:54,405
Sehemu ya 5: Misingi ya Mazungumzo ya Kila Siku ya Kijapani / Mazungumzo ya Kila Siku ya Kijapani

131
00:06:54,405 --> 00:06:57,746
Samahani, ndugu mkubwa.

132
00:06:57,770 --> 00:07:01,645
Sasa, una muda kidogo?

133
00:07:01,668 --> 00:07:05,812
Ndiyo, nini kilichotokea?

134
00:07:05,835 --> 00:07:10,809
Nimeusahau kalamu yangu, naomba unipe moja.

135
00:07:10,833 --> 00:07:15,333
Tafadhali, chukua hii.

136
00:07:15,356 --> 00:07:18,023
Asante.

137
00:07:18,046 --> 00:07:23,279
Sijui jinsi ya kuandika hati hii.

138
00:07:23,302 --> 00:07:28,136
Andika jina lako na anwani hapa.

139
00:07:28,159 --> 00:07:33,276
Samahani, nilikosea kusikia kwa sababu ulikuwa unaongea upesi sana.

140
00:07:33,299 --> 00:07:36,766
Tafadhali sema tena.

141
00:07:36,789 --> 00:07:42,357
Tafadhali andika jina lako na anwani hapa.

142
00:07:42,380 --> 00:07:45,114
Asante.

143
00:07:45,137 --> 00:07:49,814
Unaweza kunisikia kwa kuongea polepole?

144
00:07:49,837 --> 00:07:54,424
Samahani, nitahifadhi usikivu.

145
00:07:54,448 --> 00:07:57,000
Nimemaliza kuandika.

146
00:07:57,023 --> 00:08:00,598
Ni nini kinachofuata?

147
00:08:00,621 --> 00:08:04,495
Tafadhali nakili hii.

148
00:08:04,519 --> 00:08:09,064
Unaweza kunionyesha jinsi ya kutumia mashine ya nakala?

149
00:08:09,087 --> 00:08:13,067
Bonyeza kitufe hiki tu.

150
00:08:13,091 --> 00:08:15,443
Nimeelewa.

151
00:08:15,466 --> 00:08:20,499
Aa, uchapaji umekwama.

152
00:08:20,522 --> 00:08:24,089
Unaweza kunisaidia?

153
00:08:24,113 --> 00:08:27,868
Labda karatasi imefungika.

154
00:08:27,892 --> 00:08:31,037
Subiri kidogo.

155
00:08:31,060 --> 00:08:34,033
Umenisaidia sana.

156
00:08:34,057 --> 00:08:37,390
Asante sana kwa msaada wako.

157
00:08:37,413 --> 00:08:42,530
Hapana, kuna swali lolote lingine ambalo hujui?

158
00:08:42,554 --> 00:08:46,335
Kwa sasa, vyote viko sawa.

159
00:08:46,359 --> 00:08:50,826
Samahani, naweza kupumzika kesho?

160
00:08:50,849 --> 00:08:56,356
Eeh, kesho kuna mkutano muhimu!

161
00:08:56,380 --> 00:08:59,380
Mstari wa 6: Mazungumzo ya Kupiga Picha na Kuomba Ruhusa

162
00:08:59,380 --> 00:09:01,928
Samahani.

163
00:09:01,951 --> 00:09:06,534
Unaweza kunipigia picha, tafadhali?

164
00:09:06,558 --> 00:09:10,355
Ndiyo, hakuna shida.

165
00:09:10,378 --> 00:09:13,745
Nipatie kamera yako.

166
00:09:13,768 --> 00:09:17,753
Bonyeza kitufe hiki.

167
00:09:17,777 --> 00:09:20,158
Ndiyo.

168
00:09:20,181 --> 00:09:23,348
Cheese!

169
00:09:23,372 --> 00:09:27,451
Tupige picha nyingine?

170
00:09:27,474 --> 00:09:30,049
Asante.

171
00:09:30,073 --> 00:09:35,206
Naweza kupiga picha nawe?

172
00:09:35,229 --> 00:09:38,422
Nami?

173
00:09:38,446 --> 00:09:42,512
Ndiyo, kwa furaha.

174
00:09:42,535 --> 00:09:45,969
Imekuwa kumbukumbu nzuri.

175
00:09:45,992 --> 00:09:51,512
Samahani, naweza kuingia ndani ya ngome hiyo?

176
00:09:51,535 --> 00:09:56,108
Huko unahitaji tiketi.

177
00:09:56,131 --> 00:10:00,165
Ninunua tiketi wapi?

178
00:10:00,188 --> 00:10:05,093
Unaweza kununua katika jengo jeupe huko.

179
00:10:05,116 --> 00:10:09,434
Naweza kupata brosha kwa Kiingereza?

180
00:10:09,457 --> 00:10:12,957
Zipo katika ofisi ya mapokezi.

181
00:10:12,980 --> 00:10:17,332
Kuna mwongozo kwa Kijapani?

182
00:10:17,356 --> 00:10:21,822
Kuna ziara ya bure kuanzia saa sita asubuhi.

183
00:10:21,845 --> 00:10:25,412
Ningependa kushiriki.

184
00:10:25,435 --> 00:10:31,303
Mizigo yangu ni nzito, kuna kabati za kuweka vitu?

185
00:10:31,327 --> 00:10:35,560
Iko karibu na kituo cha treni.

186
00:10:35,583 --> 00:10:39,766
Huu mahali hufungua hadi saa ngapi?

187
00:10:39,790 --> 00:10:43,157
Hufungua hadi saa kumi na moja jioni.

188
00:10:43,180 --> 00:10:45,857
Nimeelewa.

189
00:10:45,880 --> 00:10:50,813
Je, naweza kula chakula changu kwenye benchi?

190
00:10:50,836 --> 00:10:53,136
Ndiyo.

191
00:10:53,159 --> 00:10:56,992
Una uhuru wa kula na kunywa hapa.

192
00:10:57,015 --> 00:11:00,015
Sehemu ya 7: Kutafuta Hospitali na Kueleza Dalili

193
00:11:00,015 --> 00:11:02,720
Samahani.

194
00:11:02,743 --> 00:11:07,043
Tafadhali, nipeleke hospitali inayokuwa karibu.

195
00:11:07,066 --> 00:11:09,933
Una shida gani?

196
00:11:09,957 --> 00:11:13,635
Uso wako unaonekana mbaya.

197
00:11:13,658 --> 00:11:18,092
Tangu jana ninaumwa na kichwa.

198
00:11:18,115 --> 00:11:21,233
Je, una homa pia?

199
00:11:21,256 --> 00:11:25,638
Ndiyo, nina homa kidogo.

200
00:11:25,662 --> 00:11:29,095
Hiyo ni mbaya sana.

201
00:11:29,118 --> 00:11:32,230
Daktari wa magonjwa ya ndani atakuwa bora.

202
00:11:32,254 --> 00:11:36,921
Je, kuna daktari anayeongea Kiingereza?

203
00:11:36,944 --> 00:11:42,112
Kliniki karibu na kituo cha treni, wao wanazungumza Kiingereza.

204
00:11:42,135 --> 00:11:44,841
Asante.

205
00:11:44,864 --> 00:11:48,097
Nitakwenda huko.

206
00:11:48,120 --> 00:11:51,075
Endelea kwa tahadhari.

207
00:11:51,099 --> 00:11:53,766
Samahani.

208
00:11:53,789 --> 00:11:56,822
Je, ninaweza kupata matibabu?

209
00:11:56,845 --> 00:11:59,482
Je, ni mara yako ya kwanza?

210
00:11:59,506 --> 00:12:03,039
Tafadhali nionyeshe kadi yako ya bima.

211
00:12:03,062 --> 00:12:07,129
Je, naweza kutumia kadi ya bima ya Japani?

212
00:12:07,152 --> 00:12:10,618
Ndiyo, unaweza kutumia.

213
00:12:10,641 --> 00:12:13,880
Tafadhali jaza fomu ya maswali.

214
00:12:13,903 --> 00:12:19,237
Ninaona kichefuchefu, naomba niruhusiwe kupumzika kidogo.

215
00:12:19,260 --> 00:12:23,244
Tafadhali kulala kwenye kitanda hiki.

216
00:12:23,267 --> 00:12:30,100
Daktari, nitapumzika kazi, tafadhali andikia cheti cha matibabu.

217
00:12:30,123 --> 00:12:32,390
Nimeelewa.

218
00:12:32,413 --> 00:12:35,772
Nitakupa dawa.

219
00:12:35,796 --> 00:12:39,671
Tafadhali nipe dawa ya kupunguza maumivu.

220
00:12:39,694 --> 00:12:43,796
Tumia dawa hii baada ya kila chakula.

221
00:12:43,820 --> 00:12:46,453
Upolee.

222
00:12:46,476 --> 00:12:49,643
Asante sana.

223
00:12:49,666 --> 00:12:52,666
Sehemu ya 8: Jinsi ya Kutenda Wakati Mfuko Wako Umeibiwa

224
00:12:52,666 --> 00:12:56,536
Samahani, nisaidie tafadhali!

225
00:12:56,559 --> 00:12:57,559
Una shida gani?

226
00:12:57,582 --> 00:13:00,249
Tulia.

227
00:13:00,272 --> 00:13:04,505
Mfuko wangu umeibiwa.

228
00:13:04,528 --> 00:13:05,528
Eeh!

229
00:13:05,552 --> 00:13:08,785
Hiyo ni mbaya sana.

230
00:13:08,808 --> 00:13:09,808
Tafadhali piga simu polisi mara moja.

231
00:13:09,831 --> 00:13:14,164
Simu yangu pia ilikuwa ndani ya mfuko.

232
00:13:14,187 --> 00:13:17,487
Nipatie simu yako tafadhali.

233
00:13:17,510 --> 00:13:21,344
Sawa, hii ndiyo.

234
00:13:21,367 --> 00:13:22,367
Nambari ya polisi ni 110.

235
00:13:22,390 --> 00:13:27,423
Halo, mfuko wangu umeibiwa.

236
00:13:27,446 --> 00:13:30,746
Polisi, ndio.

237
00:13:30,769 --> 00:13:31,769
Umeibiwa wapi?

238
00:13:31,792 --> 00:13:32,792
Nilikuwa nimeiacha kwenye choo cha kituo cha treni, nikarejea haikuwa pale.

239
00:13:32,816 --> 00:13:33,816
Kuna nini ndani ya mfuko?

240
00:13:33,839 --> 00:13:38,552
Pesa na pasipoti zilikuwa ndani.

241
00:13:38,575 --> 00:13:39,575
Je, kadi ya mkopo ilikuwa ndani?

242
